\id EPH - Mupun NT
\h Afisus
\toc3 Afis
\toc2 Afisus
\toc1 Pwoo ɗe Pool ran nen Afisus mo
\mt2 Pwoo ɗe Pool ran nen
\mt1 Afisus Mo
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Pool laalep Kristi shi rǝɓet Naan, shindǝm pee nen Naan ɗe mo nɗǝǝn nyil Afisus, ɗe mo shinzeen nJesu Kristi azeen-nzeen.
\v 2 Ɗeret kǝ ryang mǝ Naan puun fun kǝ Daa fun Jesu Kristi mo tong ashak kǝ wun.
\s1 Ɗeret Ɗe Mo a Mǝ // Riin nƊǝǝn Kristi
\p 
\v 3 Mu pǝlang Naan puun, kǝ Daa fun Jesu Kristi, ɗewur le ɗeret wur nkaa mun, shi koo a ɗeret ɗeɗangyi ɗe nǝ a mǝ Riin nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan mo, shi Kristi.
\v 4 Akuɗang Naan wur leyil nǝ, ɓe wur kǝ ten bǝlǝp mun, mbǝkǝ mu ɗee a mǝ wur nɗǝǝn Kristi, mbǝkǝ mu ɗee ɗe a ɗeɓang nɗǝǝn wal mbǝɗe baa mee shikbish ɗi ntoom nwur kas.
\p 
\v 5 Naan kǝ ten sat nee, nɗǝǝn Jesu Kristi, ɓe ɗyin nle kǝ mun ɗee a jep wur mo. Ɗesǝ nǝ put a nɗǝǝn pan mǝ retnyit wur.
\v 6 Wu yit kǝ mun kwoop wur mbǝ ɗeɗes mǝ yit naajeel nwur, ɗewur shìn mmun nzuum nɗǝǝn Làa wur ɗewur wal wur.
\v 7 Mbǝɗe a shi muut Kristi ɗangɓe mo fween mun, shii mǝnǝ a nee, mo fwo shikbish fun mo mmun. Yit naajeel nNaan nǝ ɗes zam,
\v 8 ɗewur ɗoo nǝ nkaa mun ɗes, kǝ seen kǝ manshii mbii mo jir.
\v 9 Yaksǝ Naan wur le kǝ mun man mbii ɗe mo a sǝsok mǝ pan wur mo, nciit-nciit kǝ pan wur ɗewur kǝ ten le nǝ, kǝ nǝ ɗee a ɗegǝgam nɗǝǝn Kristi.
\v 10 Mbii ɗe Naan wur kǝ ten sat nee, wuɗyin ncìn mo katɗang pee nǝ wul. Ɓe Naan wur njì kǝ mbii ɗewur kǝ ten le mo nɗǝǝn nyil ɗesǝ ashak, kǝ ɗe mo nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan kǝ ɗe mo nɗǝǝn nyil ɗesǝ jir, ɓe Kristi wur nɗee a káa mmo jir.
\v 11 Mon cìn mbii mo jir a nciit-nciit kǝ mbii ɗe Naan wur kǝ ten sat nǝ wuɗin cìn mo. Naan wur ten bǝlǝp mun, kǝ mun ɗee a nen wur mo nɗǝǝn Kristi nciit-nciit kǝ pan wur. Mbii mo ɗes aasǝ, nciit-nciit kǝ mbii ɗewur kǝ ten sat nǝ wuɗin cìn mo pǝgyet ɗi nshee.
\v 12 Mun ɗe mu shee canciin nkaa Kristi, wu yit kǝ mun kwoop Naan mbǝ ɗeɗes wur.
\v 13 A wun zak, wu ɗee a nen Naan mo kaaɗi wu kǝlǝng pwoo ɗe azeen nǝ. Pwoo ɗeret ɗe nǝ jì ɓam wun, kaaɗe wu shinzeen nKristi sǝ, ɓe Naan wur kǝ le sar wur nkaa wun, kǝ nwun ɗee ɗe a mǝ wur. Kaaɗe wur shin Riin Ɗeɓang nǝ nwun nciit-nciit kǝ mbii ɗewur kǝ ten sat sǝ.
\v 14 Riin Ɗeɓang ɗe Naan wur shin nǝ mun, wur ɗee a mbii ɗenshee ɗe nǝ kám mun nǝ, mu lap mbii ɗe Naan ten sat nǝ wuɗyin shìn nen wur mo. Ɗesǝ nǝ kám mun nǝ, Naan wur shínpee nen ɗe mo a mǝwur mo, yit kǝ mu kwoop Ɗehai wur ɗi.
\s1 Ɗangnaan Pool
\p 
\v 15 Mbǝ mbii ɗesǝ, ɓe yool mparpuus ɗe wen kǝlǝng pwoo nkaa shinzeen fuu nǝ nɗǝǝn Daa Jesu, kǝ wal fuu nǝ mbǝ nen Naan mo jir,
\v 16 ɓe baa wen kǝn nook pǝlang Naan mbǝ wun kas. Wen kǝn pan wun nɗǝǝn ɗangnaan fen mo.
\v 17 Wen kǝn ɗang pǝ Naan kǝ Daa fun Jesu Kristi, puun ɗehai shidaar-shidaar nee, ɗewur nshin Riin nwun, kǝ wur le nwun ɗee a nenseen mo, kǝ woo man mǝ Naan nwun rǝret hakyeng.
\v 18 Yit kǝ pǝtuup fuu mo wang ɗi, kǝ wu naan pee ɓang wur ɗi, mbǝkǝ wu man mbii ɗe wuu canciin ɗe ke ɗewur kǝ ten pǝrep wun mbǝ nǝ, kǝ kop ɗewur nshin nen wur mo.
\v 19 Baa mee ngwe mmak kám ɗeɗes wur, ɗe nǝ nkaa cìn ɗak nɗǝǝn mun kas, mun nen ɗe mu shinzeen wur. Iiko ɗe nǝ nkaa cìn ɗak nɗǝǝn mun, nǝ nciit-nciit kǝ ɗeɗes mǝ ɓal wur,
\v 20 ɗe gyet wur cìn ɗak kǝ nǝ, mbǝkǝ wur yool ɗe kǝ Kristi a peemúut, kǝ nNaan wur le kǝ Kristi kàa tong nsarse wur nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan.
\v 21 Kristi wur met mɓal mishkoom mo jir, kǝ iiko, kǝ ɓal, kǝ ɗes mǝ se mishkoom mo jir. Sǝm wur nǝ met koor sǝm mo jir. Baa a nɗǝǝn ɓit ɗeyaksǝ ɓejee ɗak kas, ɗangɓe kǝ nɗǝǝn ɓit ɗe mo ndung jì akyeen.
\v 22 Naan wur kǝ ten le mbii mo jir ndershii wur, kǝzak wur le wur ɗee a káa mbii mo jir mbǝ Ekǝlisya nǝ.
\v 23 Kuur nendǝm nɗang wur mo, a shin wur, ɗe mo gam kǝ wur shikáa wur, ɗewur gam mbii mo jir, koo a nɗǝǝn ar ɗeɗangyi
\c 2
\s1 Wuu Kat Seen nƊǝǝn Kristi
\p 
\v 1 Gyet nyam ɓe, wun a ɗemǝmurep nɗǝǝn tep waar kǝ shikbish fuu mo.
\v 2 Gyet nciit kǝ mǝnǝ, ɓe wuu mwaan a nɗǝǝn coor ɗebish mǝ yil ɗesǝ, kǝ nwun kǝlǝng a ɗoo mǝ mishkoom ɓal kǝ riin ɗe mo nɗǝǝn kut mo, riin ɗe nǝ pǝ cin dak nkaa nen ɗe mo cii cìn ɗyen Naan.
\v 3 Gyet mu tong a kaa mo sǝ, nɗǝǝn coor mǝ nan fun mo. Kǝ gyet mu cìn mbii ɗe mu naa mo shang nnan fun mo, kǝ pan mǝ pǝtuup fun mo zak. ɗang nɗǝǝn tong fun, kaa koor gurum mo sǝ, ɓe dǝ mu ten mu ɗee a ɗe mun nshwaajeel mbǝ tuup Naan.
\v 4 Ɗang mbǝɗe kussuk Naan kǝ wal wur nǝ ɗes zam,
\v 5 ɓe jir ɗe gyet mun a ɗemǝmurep nɗǝǝn shikbish fun mo, ɓe wur le kǝ mu kat seen ashak kǝ Kristi. Nǝ a mbǝ yit naajeel Naan, ɗangɓe mu kat ɓam.
\v 6 Naan wur nle kǝ mun yool ashak kǝ Kristi, kǝ wur le kǝ mun tong ashak kǝ wur nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan mbǝ sǝm kǝ Kristi Jesu.
\v 7 nƊǝǝn ɓit ɗe mo pǝ jì, ɓe wur nkám mmun ɗes shi ɗeɗes wur ɗe baa mee gurum mak kám nǝ kas. Ɗesǝ nǝ a yit naajeel wur ɗeɗes mbǝ mun nɗǝǝn Kristi Jesu.
\v 8 A mbǝ yit naajeel Naan, ɗangɓe wu kat ɓam, mbǝɗe wu shinzeen. Baa wu kat ɓam ɗesǝ nǝ a mbǝ mee ɗak ɗeret ɗe wu cìn kas, nǝ a zuum mǝ Naan.
\v 9 Baa nǝ a mbǝ mǝnǝ ɗak kas. Mpeemǝnǝ, ɓe taji mee gurum ɗiyeepkáa wur kas.
\v 10 A Naan wur le mun shi sar wur, kaaɗe mun ɗe sǝ, ɗangɓe yaksǝ nɗǝǝn Kristi, ɓe wur le mun a mbǝ cìn ɗak ɗeret mo, ɗewur kǝ ten ɗak nǝ le mbǝ mun, mbǝkǝ mun cìn mo ɗi.
\s1 Mun Jir A Ɗemǝndong nƊǝǝn Kristi
\p 
\v 11 Taji wu mundǝr kas, nǝ, gyet nyam ɓe wun a nen ɗe baa mo làa wun a nen Yahudi mo kas. Ɓe gyet nen Yahudi ɗe dǝ mo lesut a nen ɗe mo can mo nɗǝǝn nan shi sar gurum mo, moo pet wun a nen ɗe nsuluk mo.
\v 12 Taji wu mundǝr kas nǝ, gyet mɓít mǝnǝ mo, ɓe baa wu kus kǝ Kristi kas, kǝ baa gyet wu man Naan kas. Gyet mo shwat wun nɗǝǝn jep mǝ nen Yahudi mo, kǝ gyet wun a mǝzep mo. Mbǝɗe Naan kǝ ten ɓǝlemcuk shi toom, kǝ baa gyet wun kǝ mee mbii canciin nɗǝǝn yil nǝ kas.
\v 13 Amma, yaksǝ nɗǝǝn Kristi Jesu, ɓe wun ɗe gyet wu jong, mo kǝ jì kǝ wun kus, shi toom Kristi.
\v 14 A Kristi jì kǝ tongryang mmun, ɓe wur le kǝ nen Yahudi mo ɗee a ɗemǝndong kǝ nen ɗe baa mo a nen Yahudi mo kas. Wur shirip kok ɗe gyet nǝ ɓàk mun, mbǝkǝ mun ɗee ɗi a shaarshak.
\v 15 Wur mang Wàar nen Yahudi mo baa kǝnǝ aku, mbǝkǝ wur waa le gurum ɗepwoo mo ɗe nɗǝǝn ɗang ɗevǝl sǝ mo. Ɗe a nɗǝǝn ar ɗesǝ, ɓe wur jì kǝ tongryang.
\v 16 A shi muut wur nkaa shiyeepyoom, ɓe wur tu mbii ɗe nǝ jì kǝ ciishak ngurum mo. A shi shiyeepmúut wur, ɓe wur ɓàl ɗang mo shini-shini, kǝ mo ɗee a ɗemǝndong nɗǝǝn Naan.
\v 17 Jesu wur jì satpwoo, mǝ ryang nwun. Wun nen ɗe gyet wu jong kǝ Naan, kǝzak, wur jì kǝ pwoo nǝ nen ɗe gyet mo kus kǝ Naan zak.
\v 18 A nɗǝǝn Kristi ɓe mun gurum jir, mu mak jì nɗǝǝn Riin ɗemǝndong pǝ puun fun ɗi.
\v 19 Mbǝmǝnǝ, ɓe yaksǝ, wun nen ɗe baa wun a nen Yahudi mo kas, baa wu kuɗi a mǝzep koo pǝkor mo kas. Yaksǝ wun a ɗemǝndong kǝ jepyil mǝ nen Naan mo, kǝ nwun ɗee a jeplu mǝ Naan mo zak.
\v 20 Mo ɗyik wun a nkaa kuk ɗe jeplep kǝ Jesu mo, kǝ nensatpwoo Naan mo kǝ ten ɗyik nǝ. Jesu Kristi wur shikáa wur, a nghǝk ɗeɗes mǝ kwang lu nǝ.
\v 21 A nɗǝǝn wur, ɓe jir koor lu nǝ kǝkàa nkaa wur, kǝ a wur le kǝ lu nǝ wurang, kǝ nǝ ɗee a lu ɗeɓang mǝ Daa.
\v 22 A nɗǝǝn wur, ɓe mo ɗyik wun, kǝ nwun ɗee a pee ɗi Naan wur tong ɗi, shi riin wur.
\c 3
\s1 Ɗak Ɗe Pool Cìn // mBǝ Gurum Mo
\p 
\v 1 A mbǝ ɗesǝ, ɓe wen Pool, an a shishoot mbǝ Kristi Jesu, mbǝ wun nen ɗe baa wun a nen Yahudi mo kas.
\v 2 Azeen-nzeen wu man nee, nɗǝǝn ɗeret Naan, ɓe wur shin ɗak ɗesǝ nǝ nwen, mbǝkǝ nghan cìn ɗi mbǝ wun.
\v 3 Naan wur woo mbii ɗesǝsok mo nwen ɗewur kǝ ten sat nǝ wuɗin ncìn nwen. Wen kǝn ran pwoo nwun lee nkaa nǝ.
\v 4 Katɗang wu tang mbii ɗe ghan kǝn ran nǝ, ɓe wun mmanshii mman fen, nkaa mbii ɗesǝsok mǝ Kristi.
\v 5 Gyet nyam, ɓe baa mo woo mbii ɗesǝsok nǝ mo ngurum mo kas, amma yaksǝ ɓe Naan wur kǝ woo nǝ agaak pee jeplep Jesu Kristi mo, kǝ nensatpwoo Naan ɗeɓang mo, shi Riin wur ɗeɓang.
\v 6 Mbii ɗesǝsok nǝ a nee, nen ɗe baa mo a nen Yahudi mo kas, yaksǝ nɗǝǝn pwoo ɗeret nǝ, ɓe mo kat ɗeret mǝ Naan ashak kǝ nen Yahudi nǝ mo. Kǝzak yaksǝ, ɓe nen ɗe baa mo a nen Yahudi mo kas, mo ɗee a mbii ɗemǝndong. Mo mak sekop nɗǝǝn mbii ɗe Naan wur kǝ ten cweer nǝ, nwur gam nǝ nɗǝǝn Kristi.
\p 
\v 7 A mbee pwoo ɗeret ɗesǝ, ɓe Naan wur nle kǝ ghan ɗee a ngucìn ɗak wur, nciit kǝ zuum ɗeret mǝ yit naajeel wur ɗewur kǝcin nwen, ɗe nǝ nkaa cìn ɗak nɗǝǝn ɓal wur.
\v 8 Koo ɗe ghan a ɗetaakat met jir nɗǝǝn nen Naan mo, amma Naan wur cin ɗak ɗesǝ nǝ nwen, ɗe nǝ satpwoo ɗeret nǝ mbǝ nen ɗe baa mo a nen Yahudi mo kas. Pwoo nkaa long Kristi ɗe baa nǝ kǝ peekyes kas.
\v 9 Kǝzak, mbǝkǝ nghan le kǝ gurum mo manshii mbii ɗesǝsok mǝ Naan mo ɗi, ɗe Naan ɗewur le mbii mo nɗǝǝn nyil nǝ jir, ɓe wur kǝ ten sok mbii ɗesǝ nǝ mbee ɓit mo ɗes.
\v 10 Pan wur ɗesǝ nǝ, yaksǝ nɗǝǝn nendǝm nɗang wur mo, ɓe ɗeɗes mǝ seen wur nǝ ɗee agaak nɗǝǝn ar mo shini-shini, pǝ nenlep Naan mo kǝ iiko ɗe mo nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan
\v 11 Nciit-nciit kǝ mbii ɗe Naan wur kǝ ten sat nee, wuɗin ncìn nǝ shindǝm ngaa-ngaa, ɗewur gam nǝ nɗǝǝn ɓalkaa fun ashak kǝ Kristi Jesu Daa fun.
\v 12 Kǝ shinzeen fun nɗǝǝn wur, ɓe mu katɓal mpǝtuup, kǝ mu dǝm ɗe ntoom Naan, baa a shi kǝǝrmuut kas.
\v 13 Wen kǝn ɗang pǝ wun, taji kwak fuu mo murep kas, mbǝɗe jir shawaajeel ɗe an nkaa shwaa nǝ a mbǝ wun. Shwaajeel fen nǝ kǝkoop nǝ pee wun ɗi.
\s1 Ɗangnaan mBǝ Nen Afisus Mo
\p 
\v 14 A mbǝmǝnǝ, ɓe an kǝn kurum ntoom puun,
\v 15 a mbǝ wur, ɓe koo a weyi ɗe mo nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan kǝ ɗe mo nɗǝǝn nyil ɗesǝ moo kat sǝm wur.
\v 16 Wen kǝn ɗang pǝ Naan nɗǝǝn long wur ɗeɗes, mbǝkǝ wur shin iiko ɗe nwun nɗǝǝn Riin wur. Mbǝkǝ nwun katɓal ɗe nɗǝǝn pǝtuup fuu mo.
\v 17 Mɓe kǝ Kristi wur tong nɗǝǝn pǝtuup fuu mo, mbǝɗe wu shinzeen wur. Wu shamseen, kǝ nwun ɗar nkaa kuk ɗe nǝ a wal.
\v 18 Mbǝkǝ nwun, ashak kǝ nen Naan mo, ɓe wu man kaam, kǝ shwal, kǝ wurang, kǝ jurum mǝ wal mǝ Kristi ɗi.
\v 19 Kǝzak, mbǝkǝ wu man wal mǝ Kristi ɗe nǝ met nkoor man mo jir, mbǝkǝ wu gam ɗi kǝ man Naan nɗǝǝn pǝtuup fuu mo.
\v 20 Yaksǝ, pee wur, ɗewur kǝ iiko ɗe nǝ cìn ɗak nɗǝǝn mun, met mbii ɗe mu mak ɗang mo, koo pan ɗe mo nɗǝǝn pǝtuup fun.
\v 21 Ɗeɗes nǝ ɗee a mǝ Naan nɗǝǝn nendǝm ndang wur mo, kǝ nɗǝǝn Kristi Jesu mbǝ pǝ mo jir, yool yaksǝ kǝ, har ngaa-ngaa. Nǝ a kǝsǝ.
\c 4
\s1 Mo Ɓàl Mun Kǝ Fwooshin Kristi
\p 
\v 1 Wen ɗe an a shishoot mbǝ sǝm Daa. Wen kǝn ɗang pǝ wun, mbǝkǝ wu mwaan-mwaan ɗe mo lapshak kǝ petpee ɗe Naan wur kǝ pǝrep wun mbǝ nǝ.
\v 2 Wu sham kǝ káa fuu mo koo pǝranyi. Wu cìn mbii mo nɗǝǝn ɗyen, kǝ wun gung zak. Wu kám wal fuu mo agaak, kǝ nwun fwangshak zak.
\v 3 Wu gung, kǝ nwun tap ɗe kǝ ɓalkaa ɗe Riin wur shin nwun, shi tongryang ɗe nǝ ɓàl wun ashak.
\v 4 Shin nǝ a mǝndong, kǝ Riin nǝ mǝndong ɓejee. Kaaɗi mo kǝ pǝrep wun, nɗǝǝn canciin mǝndong nkaa mbii ɗe mo kǝ pet wun mbǝ nǝ.
\v 5 Daa a mǝndong, shinzeen nǝ a mǝndong, baptisma nǝ a mǝndong,
\v 6 Naan a mǝndong, ɗewur a puun fun jir. Wur met mbii mo jir, kǝ a wur cìn ɗak nɗǝǝn mun jir, kǝ a wur nɗǝǝn mun jir zak.
\v 7 Ɗang koo a weyi nɗǝǝn mun, ɓe wur kǝ lap ɗeret nciit-nciit kǝ zuum kǝ Kristi.
\v 8 Kaaɗe mo kǝ ran nɗǝǝn ɓǝǝt haal Naan sǝ nǝnee,
\q1 <<Kaaɗe Kristi wur kaa aɗeng,
\q2 ɓe wur pan kǝrem
\q1 ɗeyiyak mo ɗes ashak kǝ wur,
\q2 kǝ wur shin zuum ngurum mo zak.>>
\m 
\v 9 Yaksǝ, ɓe nǝnee, <<wur kaa aɗeng >> ɓe shii mǝnǝ a mii? Shii mǝnǝ nee, nshee ɓe wur sham nɗǝǝn jurum kǝ peekyes kǝ yil ɗesǝ.
\v 10 Mbǝmǝnǝ, gwar ɗe gyet wur sham, a wur a gwar ɗewur kaa aɗeng-ɗeng a kǝkyeen ɗengnaan mo, mbǝkǝ wur gam ɗeng kǝ yil jir.
\v 11 A wur shìn zuum ngurum mbǝkǝ npak mo ɗee ɗi, a jeplep mo, kǝ npak mo ɗee a nensatpwoo Naan mo, kǝ npak mo ɗee ɗi a nenkop pwoo Naan mo, kǝ npak mo ɗee ɗi a Pasto mo, kǝ npak mo ɗee ɗi a nenkám kam mo zak.
\v 12 Wur shin zuum ɗesǝ mo, a mbǝkǝ nǝ ɗak nen Naan mo ɗe, mbǝ ɓamshak, kǝ mbǝkǝ mo ɗyik fwoshik kǝ Kristi ɗi.
\v 13 Nǝ aasǝ, ɓe mun jir, mun nyool mu ɗee a ɗemǝndong nɗǝǝn shinzeen fun, kǝ man fun ɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn Làa Naan. Mun nyool mu ɗee a nen ɗe kǝ man mo, Mbǝkǝ mun wul mbǝ gam ɗeɗes mǝ Kristi.
\v 14 Ɓe baa mu kuɗi a jep ɗeɗyeen mo kas mǝnǝ, ɗe mo nnum mun shindǝm sǝ, Mbǝkǝ mo mang mun pán, shi koo a kyaan kám ɗeɗangyi kas. Mo a nenseen mo ɗe mo a korong mbǝ ɓǝrǝm ɗung.
\v 15 Akoppee mǝnǝ nǝ ret kǝ mun sat zeen nǝ nɗǝǝn nwal. Nǝ ret kǝ mun wurang nɗǝǝn mbii mo jir, nɗǝǝn Kristi ɗewur a káa fun.
\v 16 A mbǝ wur, ɗangɓe koo a ɓeep ɗeɗangyi, mo shini-shini, mo tap ɓàl ashak, kǝ koo a peeɓal ɗeɗangyi, nǝ katɓal a nɗǝǝn wur. Katɗang koo a ɓeep ɗeɗangyi nǝ kǝ cìn ɗak war rǝret, ɓe fwoshik nǝ nwurang, kǝ nǝ ɗyik set ɗi nɗǝǝn nwal zak.
\s1 Seen Ɗepwoo nƊǝǝn Kristi
\p 
\v 17 nƊǝǝn sǝm Daa, ɓe nkǝn satpwoo wun shiɓal nǝ, taji wu sat a ntong kaa nen ɗe baa mo a nen Yahudi mo kas sǝ, ɗe pan mo a ɗebuu.
\v 18 Pan ɗe nɗǝǝn pǝtuup mo, nǝ a mǝ peenkwoo, baa mo kǝ mee lǝɓet nɗǝǝn seen ɗe Naan shin kas, mbǝɗe baa mo kǝ mee man kas, kǝ mo ɗee a nencinshik mo.
\v 19 Baa mo kuɗi kǝ naashweep kǝ mee mbii kas. Mo fes shínkáa fur mo mbǝ cìn mbii ɗebish mo, kǝ moo coor mbǝ cìn koo a mbii ɗebish ɗeɗangyi. Baa moo kǝ mee yaasut kas.
\p 
\v 20 Amma baa a mbii ɗe wun wu kám pee Kristi ɗe mǝnǝ kas!
\v 21 Mo sat nnǝ, wuu ten wu kǝlǝng pwoo nkaa wur, kǝ mmoo kám nwun zeen ɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn Jesu.
\v 22 Wu shwat suk ɗesǝǝr nǝ mo wu baa kǝ mo aku, ɗe dǝ moo nnum wun nɗǝǝn coor mǝ nan sǝ.
\v 23 Nǝ a tǝng kǝ npǝtuup fuu mo kǝ pan fuu mo ɗee a ɗepwoo,
\v 24 Kǝzak, nǝ a tǝng kǝ wu jwal fwoshik ɗepwoo nǝ mo, ɗe Naan wur ɗak mǝnǝ shikaa fin sǝ, kǝ nǝ woo káa nnǝ agaak nɗǝǝn seen ɗe nǝ azeen-nzeen ɗe nǝ a ɗeret kǝ ɗeɓang.
\p 
\v 25 Mbǝmǝnǝ, wu baa kǝ ɗung nɗǝǝn wun, kǝ koo a weyi ɓe wur sat azeen ngǝnǝǝn wur ɓejee ɗak. Mbǝɗe mun a ɗemǝndong kǝ shak nɗǝǝn Kristi.
\v 26 Katɗang wu langtuup, ɓe taji wu cìn shikbish kas. Taji puus shamru, ɓe wun ɗe nkaa langtuup kas.
\v 27 Taji wu shínpee ngujwaan kas.
\v 28 Ngwe ɗe wur cìn wat, ɓe taji wur baa cìn ɗe kas, ɗangɓe nǝ ret kǝ wur cìn ɗak ɗeret shi sar wur, mbǝkǝ wur mak cin mee mbii ɗe nen ɗe mo mɓut njeel
\v 29 Taji pwoo ɗebish mo put nɗǝǝn pwoo fuu mo kas, ɗangɓe ɗang a mbii ɗeret mo, ɗe mon nɗyik wun, kaaɗi nǝ tap ret kǝ pee nǝ sǝ. Mbǝkǝ nǝ jì ɗe kǝ ɗeret nen ɗe moo kǝlǝng nǝ.
\v 30 Taji wu wàt pǝtuup nRiin Ɗeɓang mǝ Naan kas, wur ɗe a wur ɗee a langtǝng nǝ, wuu ɗee a ɗe fufwang mbǝ parpuus ɗe mon mɓam wun.
\v 31 Wu pwat kǝ pwoo ɗeɗeet mo, kǝ ciishak, kǝ tuup, kǝ ɓutbish, kǝ fǝlǝppee ashak kǝ cìn nyang mo jir.
\v 32 Ɗang nǝ ret kǝ nwun naajeel shak, kǝ nwun ɓam shak, kǝ nwun fwo ɗi nshak, kaaɗi Naan wur fwo ɗi nwun nɗǝǝn Kristi sǝ.
\c 5
\s1 Mwaan nƊǝǝn Peeɓang
\p 
\v 1 Kaaɗe wun a jep Naan mo ɗewur wal wun sǝ, ɓe nǝ a tǝng kǝ nwun kám shiimwaan Naan.
\v 2 Kǝzak, wu mwaan nɗǝǝn wal, kaaɗe Kristi wur wal mmun sǝ, ɓe wur shìn kaashin mbǝ mun kaa zuum kǝ mbiizuum ɗe nǝ kǝ toos shang shang pǝ Naan ɗi.
\p 
\v 3 Taji pwoo nkaa ngaa, kǝ mbii ɗebish mo, kǝ rǝɓet mbii mo pwat nɗǝǝn pwoo fuu mo kas. Mbǝɗe pwoo nkaa kaan kǝ mǝnǝ mo, baa nǝ ret kǝ mo pwat mpwoo nen Naan mo kas.
\v 4 Kǝsǝ zak, taji mee pwoo ɗebish mǝ le naashweep kǝ pwoo mǝ mwen mo, kǝ pwoo ɗebuu mo, mo pwat nɗǝǝn pwoo fuu mo kas, amma wu yit kǝn plang put pwoo fuu mo.
\v 5 Taji wu mundǝr nee, nen ɗe moo cìn ngaa, kǝ nen ɗe pan mo a ɗebish, kǝ ngutǝlǝk mo, ɓe baa mee kaan nen mǝnǝ moo mee lǝɓet mǝ sekop nɗǝǝn mulki Kristi kǝ mǝ Naan kas.
\v 6 Taji wu yit kǝ mee gurum nnum wun shi pwoo ɗebuu mo kas, mbǝɗe a mbǝ mbii mo kaa ɗesǝ mo ɓe tuup Naan nǝ taa nkaa nencii kǝlǝngpee mo.
\v 7 Mbǝmǝnǝ, taji wu ɓalkaa fuu ashak kǝ nen mǝnǝ mo kas.
\v 8 Gyet nyam, wun a nɗǝǝn peenkwoo, ɗangɓe yaksǝ wun a nɗǝǝn peeɓang, nɗǝǝn Daa. Nǝ ret kǝ wu mwaan kaa nen ɗe mo nɗǝǝn peeɓang nǝ sǝ.
\v 9 Ɗak nen ɗe mo nɗǝǝn peeɓang, nǝ a nɗǝǝn mbii ɗeret mo, kǝ ɗe ndǝre mo, kǝ zeen zak.
\v 10 Wu gung, kǝ nwun kám mbii ɗe mon nret nNaan nyit.
\v 11 Taji wu lesar fuu mo nɗǝǝn ɗak ɗe mo a mǝ peenkwoo, ɗe baa mo kǝkoop nǝ kas, ɗangɓe nǝ ret kǝ wu woo ɗak mǝnǝ mo agaak.
\v 12 Nǝ a mbii naashweep mbee satpwoo nkaa mbii ɗe moo cìn mo a sǝsok.
\v 13 Ɗang katɗang jir mbii ɗe nǝ agaak, a pee ɗe ɓang ɗi, ɓe nǝ nɗee a ɗe gurum mo mak naa nǝ. Mbǝɗe jir mbii ɗe gurum mo mak naa nǝ, ɓe nǝ a nɗǝǝn peeɓang.
\v 14 Nǝ a kaaɗi mo kǝ ran nɗǝǝn ɓǝǝt haal nNaan sǝ nǝnee,
\q1 <<Ngusaam, a mii, a yool a peemúut
\q2 Mbǝkǝ Kristi wur
\q1 shin peeɓang ɗe ngha>>
\p 
\v 15 Wu tap kǝ shiimwaan fuu mo. Taji wu mwaan kaa mwen mo sǝ kas, ɗangɓe wu mwaan kaa nen ɗe kǝ seen mo sǝ.
\v 16 Wu cìn ɗak koo a pee ɗeɗangyi, mbǝɗe teer ɗe yaksǝ nǝ mo gam kǝ mbii ɗebish mo.
\v 17 Mbǝmǝnǝ, ɓe taji wu ɗee a mwen mo kas, amma wu manshii kǝ mbii ɗe Daa wur rǝɓet kǝ nwun cìn.
\v 18 Taji wu shwaa am anab kǝ nǝ yuur wun kas, mbǝɗe mǝnǝ mak jwaan wun, amma wu ɗee a ɗegǝgam shi Riin Ɗeɓang.
\v 19 Wu sat mee pwoo kǝ shak shi kook ɗe mǝ kwoop mo, kǝ kook ɗe mo a mǝ Riin. Wu cìn kook ɗeret mo nNaan, kǝ pǝlang nɗǝǝn pǝtuup fuu mo.
\v 20 Koo pǝranyi ɓe wu plang Naan puun mbǝ mbii mo jir nɗǝǝn sǝm nDaa fun Jesu Kristi.
\s1 Mat Mo Kǝ Mish Mo
\p 
\v 21 Wu shin ɗeɗes ndǝr shak, mbǝkǝ wu shin ɗeɗes ɗi nKristi.
\v 22 Mat mo, wu shin ɗe ɗeɗes mmish fuu mo, kaaɗi wuu cìn nDaa sǝ.
\v 23 Mbǝɗe mish wur a káa mat, kaaɗi Kristi wur a káa Ekǝlisya sǝ, shii kǝ mǝnǝ a fwooshin fin kǝ wur shikáa fin a Nguɓam war zak.
\v 24 Kaaɗe Ekǝlisya war ndǝr Kristi, nǝ aasǝ zak, wun mat mo, wu shin ɗeɗes mmish fuu mo nɗǝǝn mbii mo jir.
\v 25 Mish mo, wu wal mmat fuu mo, kaaɗi Kristi wur wal Ekǝlisya nǝ sǝ, har wur shinkaa shin mbǝ war.
\v 26 Mbǝkǝ wur le war ɗee ɗi a ɗeɓang shi vwang war kǝ am, kǝ pwoo Naan.
\v 27 Mbǝkǝ wur ɗak Ekǝlisya nǝ le ɗe nshin, nɗǝǝn ɗeɗes, kǝ ɗemen, baa ashak kǝ mee rap, kǝ mee pee taakat mɓut mo kas. Mbǝkǝ mo ɗee ɗe a ɗeɓang baa kǝ mee rap kas.
\v 28 Ni ret kǝ mish mo wal mmat fur mo kaa sut sǝ. Ngwe ɗewur wal mmat wur, ɓe wur wal a nshin mǝnǝ.
\v 29 Baa mee gurum kǝ cam cii shin kas, ɗangɓe wur tap shin mbiise nnǝ, kǝ wur tap kǝ nǝ rǝret, kaaɗi Kristi wur cìn Ekǝlisya sǝ
\v 30 Mbǝɗe mun a ɓeep mǝ foshik nwur.
\v 31 A mbǝmǝnǝ, ɓe gurum wur nyit puun wur kǝ nǝǝn wur, kǝ wur ɓalkaa ɗe ashak kǝ mat wur, kǝ mo vǝl mo ɗee ɗi a ɗemǝndong.
\v 32 Ɗesǝ nǝ a mee mbii ɗeɗes ɗesǝsok. Mbii ɗe wen kǝn sat nǝ, a nkaa Kristi kǝ Ekǝlisya.
\v 33 Jir arang ɓe wu yit koo weyi wur wal mmat wur, kaa kaashin sǝ, kǝ mat war shin ɗeɗes mmish war zak.
\c 6
\s1 Jep Mo Kǝ Puun Mo
\p 
\v 1 Jep mo, wu kǝlǝng pwoo mpuun fuu mo nɗǝǝn Daa, mbǝɗe mǝnǝ a mbii ɗe ndǝre.
\v 2 <<A shin ɗeɗes mpuun fwa kǝ nǝǝn fwaa mo,>> ɗesǝ nǝ a Wàar ɗenshee ɗe mo kǝ ten le,
\v 3 <<mbǝkǝ a tong ɗi ryang, kǝ mbǝkǝ a kat teer mo ɗi ɗes nɗǝǝn nyil nǝ.>>
\v 4 Puun mo, taji wu le kǝ pǝtuup jep fuu mo wat, kǝ nǝ le kǝ mo cìn tuup kas, amma wu kyeer mo, kǝ wu kar mo nɗǝǝn kám ɗe mo a mǝ Daa Naan.
\s1 Kǝrem Mo Kǝ Nen Ɗe Ɗyel Mo
\p 
\v 5 Kǝrem mo, wu kǝlengpwoo nen ɗe moo ɗyel wun nsar fur mo. Kǝn sat a puun fuu ɗe mo a mǝ yil ɗesǝ nǝ. Wu kǝlengpwoo mo nɗǝǝn kǝǝr kǝ ɗaar shi pǝtuup mǝndong, kaaɗi wuu cìn nKristi sǝ.
\v 6 Taji wu cìn ɗak a yit gurum mo ɓejee, kǝ mo plang wun ɗe kas, amma wu cìn ɗak kaa kǝrem mǝ Kristi sǝ. Wu cìn ɗyen nNaan nɗǝǝn pǝtuup fuu mo.
\v 7 Wu cìn ɗak shi pǝtuup ɗeret, mbǝɗe wu cìn a nDaa Naan, baa a mmee gurum kas.
\v 8 Taji wu mundǝr kas nǝ, ɗak ɗeret ɗe gurum kǝ cìn mo, ɓe wur nwaa lap kwat nǝ pee Daa ɗi, koo ɗewur a kǝrem, kǝ ɗewur a laalu.
\v 9 Wun nen ɗe wun kǝ kǝrem mo wu cìn mbii ɗeret mmo zak. Taji wu wuk mo kas, mbǝɗe wu man nǝ, Daa fu kǝ moo, wur a nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, baa wur kǝ nshwatyit kas.
\s1 Leelek Naan Mo Jir
\p 
\v 10 Peekyes nǝ, wu ɗar ɓalɓal nɗǝǝn Daa nɗǝǝn iiko mǝ ɗeɗes wur.
\v 11 Wu jwal leelek ɗe Naan wur shin mo wun jir, mbǝkǝ nwun mak ɗar ɗi ɓalɓal nkaa Ngujwaan kǝ gwampee wur.
\v 12 Mbǝɗe baa mu cìn lek nǝ a nkaa gurum mo, ɗe moo nan kǝ toom kas, ɗangɓe nǝ a nkaa se mishkoom, nen iiko ɗe mo a mǝ Ngujwaan mo, nkaa se mishkoom kǝ nen peeknwoo ɗe nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan mo.
\v 13 Mbǝmǝnǝ, ɓe wu jwal leelek ɗe Naan wur nshin nwun, mbǝkǝ nwun ɗar ɗi ɓalɓal nɗǝǝn teer ɗebish mo. Mbǝkǝ taji Ngujwaan wur se koorong nkaa wun kas.
\v 14 Wu ɗar ɓalɓal shi ɗak suk, kǝ ɓwoot ɓwoon fuu mo shi zeen, kǝ cìn mbii ɗe ndǝre kaa kawung ɗe nǝ tap tuur ngurum sǝ.
\v 15 Wu jwal kwoopshii nshii fuu mo, mbǝ satpwoo ɗeret, ɗe nǝn jì kǝ tongryang.
\v 16 Koo pǝrangyi, ɓe wu mang gwat ɗe nǝ a shinzeen ashak kǝ wun, mbǝ tap pas mǝ wus ɗe gwar ɗebish nǝ wur mpwas shinji nkaa wun.
\v 17 Wu mang ɓam ɗe Naan wur cìn nwun, kaa mbiikáa shool ɗe nenlek moo lep mbǝkǝ nǝ tap káa ɗi mmo sǝ. Kǝ wu ɗyel pwoo Naan nǝ, kaa kwai ɗe Riin Ɗeɓang wur shin nwun sǝ.
\v 18 Wu ɗangnaan (leshap kǝ Naan), mbǝ mbii ɗesǝ mo shidaar-shidaar nɗǝǝn Riin. Wu tong shi gongpee, kǝzak, wu gung nɗǝǝn mbii mo jir. Wu cìn ɗangnaan (leshap kǝ Naan) mbǝ nen Naan mo jir.
\v 19 Wu ɗangnaan (leshap kǝ Naan) mbǝ ghan zak, mbǝkǝ Naan wur cìn mbii ɗe wen nsat mo ɗi, kǝ mbǝkǝ ghan sat mbii ɗesǝsok mǝ pwoo ɗeret nǝ mo, ɗe shiɓal baa a shi kǝǝrmuut kas.
\v 20 A mbǝ pwoo ɗeret nǝ, ɗang mo lep an mbǝkǝ wen sat nǝ ɗi. Ɓe wen a shishoot shi tǝsek mǝ shool yaksǝ. Jir kǝ ɗe an a shishoot, ɓe wu cìn ɗangnaan (leshap kǝ Naan), mbǝkǝ wur shinɓal ɗi nwen, kǝn satpwoo ɗeret nǝ ɗe shiɓal, kaaɗi nǝ ret kǝ wen cìn sǝ.
\s1 Tokshik Mǝ Kes Nǝ
\p 
\v 21 Tikikus ɗyemnǝǝn fun ɗe mu wal wur, ɗewur a kǝrem Daa azeen-nzeen, wur nsat mbii mo nwun jir, nkaa an, kǝ nkaa ɗak ɗe ghan nkaa cìn nǝ.
\v 22 Wen kǝn ten nlep wur shindǝm pee wun ɗe, a mbǝkǝ wur satpwoo ɗi nwun nkaa mun, mbǝkǝ nwun man tong fun ɗe, kǝ nǝ ɓam pǝtuup fuu mo ɗi zak.
\v 23 Naan puun, kǝ Daa fun Jesu Kristi shin tongryang, kǝ wal, kǝ shinzeen nɗyemnǝǝn fun mo jir.
\v 24 Ɗeret Naan nǝ ɗee ashak kǝ nen ɗe mo wal nDaa fun Jesu Kristi, shi wal ɗe baa nii peekyes kas har ngaa-ngaa.
